&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At the craft level&lt;/strong&gt;, setting the creative bar and personally shipping the highest-priority brand, campaign, product, and web work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At the systems

